description: This file contains React components related to displaying tables in the UI for an animal behavior analytics platform. It includes a video library table and a behavior events table, both of which render data-driven tables with filtering, sorting, and action buttons.

methods.name: VideoLibraryTable
methods.description: A React component that displays a table of video files with upload progress, detection status, and action buttons.

methods.name: BehaviorEventsTable
methods.description: A React component that displays a filterable and sortable table of behavior event items with different attributes.
